Name: Dateline NBC
Title: The House on Shalimar Way
Desc: Insiders speak out about the latest developments in the suspicious death of a New York woman.
LongDescription: When Leslie Neulander dies after what appears to be an accidental fall in the shower in her New York home, two friends join forces to seek justice on her behalf; insiders speak out on the latest twists and the final chapter in the case.
